name: Midaswap
intro: AMM protocol for NFTS based on Liquidity Books
introduce: Midaswap is an Automated Market Maker (AMM) protocol for NFTS based on Liquidity Book. It aims to aggregate different pricing strategies of different LPS in the same liquidity pool by combining customizable liquidity positions, Multihop Swap and other means, so as to achieve full aggregation of asset liquidity on the FT side.
